pip install opencv-python torch clip-by-openai gtts pygame numpy pillow ultralytics


opencv-python → Provides cv2 for computer vision tasks.
torch → PyTorch, required for deep learning operations.
clip-by-openai → The CLIP model from OpenAI.
gtts → Google Text-to-Speech library.
pygame → Used for handling audio (mixer).
numpy → Essential for numerical computations.
pillow → Provides PIL for image processing.
ultralytics → Required for YOLO (You Only Look Once) object detection.
